                <p class="text-xs text-amber-800 mt-1">After launching, 80% of custom features went unused.</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-amber-800">The killer feature everyone thought they needed? Used by 3 visitors total.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Step 3 -->
          <div class="bg-white border-2 border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-5">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <span class="bg-slate-800 text-white w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-black text-sm">3</span>
              <p class="text-lg font-black text-slate-900">DECISION: Budget reality</p>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-11">
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-2"><strong>What people think:</strong> Developer quote is final price</p>
              <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 mt-2">
                <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded p-3">
                  <p class="text-xs text-blue-700 font-bold">QUOTE</p>
                  <p class="text-sm font-black text-blue-900">$5,000</p>
                  <p class="text-xs text-blue-600">for custom site</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded p-3">
