                  <p class="text-sm font-black text-red-900">$15,400</p>
                  <p class="text-xs text-red-600">after changes + delays</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-600 mt-2 italic">‚Üí Every traditional project went over budget. Average overrun: 210%. AI builders: exactly $20/month.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Step 4 -->
          <div class="bg-white border-2 border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-5">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <span class="bg-slate-800 text-white w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-black text-sm">4</span>
              <p class="text-lg font-black text-slate-900">DECISION: Timeline to launch</p>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-11">
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-2"><strong>What people think:</strong> Perfect site in 3 months beats good enough today</p>
