                <ul class="text-xs text-purple-700 ml-4 mt-1 space-y-0.5">
                  <li>‚Ä¢ 8 lost funding</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ 4 had competitors launch first</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ 3 changed business models entirely</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
