              <p class="text-lg font-black text-slate-900">DECISION: Complex requirements</p>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-11">
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-2"><strong>What people think:</strong> Booking, payments, user accounts = need custom dev</p>
              <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 mt-2">
                <div class="bg-slate-100 border border-slate-300 rounded p-3">
                  <p class="text-xs text-slate-700 font-bold">AI + INTEGRATIONS</p>
