                  <p class="text-sm font-black text-slate-900">$12,000</p>
                  <p class="text-xs text-slate-600 mt-1">+ 6 weeks</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-600 mt-2 italic">‚Üí AI builders + integrations handle booking, payments, user accounts, CRM integration.</p>
            </div>
