  </div>
    <!-- REAL AI VS TRADITIONAL SUCCESS STORIES -->
    <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 mb-16">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-green-50 border-[3px] border-purple-400 p-6 md:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">Real AI vs Traditional Builder Success Stories: 12-Month Outcomes</h2>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-8 uppercase tracking-wider font-black">From 127 users who chose AI builders vs traditional methods. Time to launch, costs, and satisfaction scores.</p>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
          <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-purple-400 p-5">
